      "text": "ch4_plume_ready\r\n| where acquisition_date between (_startTime .. _endTime)\r\n| summarize AvgCH4 = round(avg(ch4), 2)\r\n    by bin(acquisition_date,\r\n        case(\r\n            datetime_diff('hour', _endTime, _startTime) <= 48,  1h,\r\n            datetime_diff('day',  _endTime, _startTime) <= 30,  1d,\r\n            7d\r\n        ))\r\n| order by acquisition_date asc\r\n| project acquisition_date, AvgCH4",
