      "text": "ch4_plume_catalog\r\n| where isnotnull(emission_rate_kg_s)\r\n    and isnotnull(area_km2)\r\n    and area_km2 > 0\r\n| extend\r\n    EmissionRateKgHr = round(emission_rate_kg_s * 3600, 2),\r\n    Confidence = case(\r\n        emission_rate_confidence == \"high\", \"high\",\r\n        emission_rate_confidence == \"low\",  \"low\",\r\n        \"unknown\"                           // catches empty string and nulls\r\n    )\r\n| project\r\n    plume_id,\r\n    area_km2,\r\n    EmissionRateKgHr,\r\n    ime_kg,\r\n    Confidence,\r\n    max_delta_ch4_ppb,\r\n    wind_speed_ms,\r\n    elongation\r\n| order by EmissionRateKgHr desc",
